{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2271603, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {"h": 1024, "w": 596}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 437233, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "", "timestamp": 1628863786, "type": "image", "url": "zt/zt4zpc2aplmrbck735gnkwbqvsrzpl2t.jpeg"}, {"cid": 2271608, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 437233, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "民主面对新冠不堪一击", "timestamp": 1628863804, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2271626, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 437233, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "感觉为大英带来繁荣的不是民主制度，天时地利人和吧。", "timestamp": 1628863923, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2271632, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 437233, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "民主只能作为政治无能的遮羞布，并无实质好处。", "timestamp": 1628863986, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2271651, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 437233, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "民主的国家连空气都带着新冠的气息", "timestamp": 1628864097, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2271666, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 437233, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "emm这样民主圣战的历史观是有点浅薄的，而且有点因果倒置。就那拿破仑来说，当时反法同盟的构成才是相对反动的吧？", "timestamp": 1628864215, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2271672, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 437233, "reply_to": 2271666, "tag": null, "text": "#434333\n“自由民主万能yao”", "timestamp": 1628864245, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2271679, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 437233, "reply_to": 2271603, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: #437136", "timestamp": 1628864318, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2271689, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 437233, "reply_to": 2271672, "tag": null, "text": "民主在人类历史上遭受过无数次挫折，不列颠的天空曾经被纳粹空军占领，凯旋门上也挂起过纳粹的十字旗，苏维埃的核弹也曾让西方人胆寒，但民主的失败总是暂时的", "timestamp": 1628864397, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2271691, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 437233, "reply_to": 2271679, "tag": null, "text": "也许“民主”是一个解，那也是个没有希望的解，科幻里会走向缸中之脑的结局那种", "timestamp": 1628864406, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2271693, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 437233, "reply_to": 2271689, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 在人类的漫长历史里，民主不断扩展自己的势力范围，专制和威权在不断地丧失领地", "timestamp": 1628864441, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2271709, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 437233, "reply_to": 2271693, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 古埃及，古希腊，古罗马，都曾有资格这么说", "timestamp": 1628864600, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2271710, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 437233, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "冷知识，民主这个口号是西方国家从苏联那里抄来的", "timestamp": 1628864609, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2271712, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 437233, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "那时他们只敢喊自由", "timestamp": 1628864628, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2271730, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 437233, "reply_to": 2271710, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 其实不是吧，三权分立早就有了", "timestamp": 1628864856, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2271731, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 437233, "reply_to": 2271710, "tag": null, "text": "当时就叫民主了", "timestamp": 1628864865, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2271732, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 437233, "reply_to": 2271691, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 民主不是为了解决什么问题而存在，它只不过符合人类爱好自由，反对特权者压迫的本性", "timestamp": 1628864869, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2271733, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 437233, "reply_to": 2271732, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 没有人喜欢被压迫，不是吗", "timestamp": 1628864884, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2271751, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 437233, "reply_to": 2271672, "tag": null, "text": "Re Francis: 难道zg就最好了？马列早就在苏联爆炸了。现在明摆着就是经济走zi，政治因为威胁统治而没变", "timestamp": 1628865052, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2271762, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 437233, "reply_to": 2271733, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 那么你所谓的民主，是从什么时候开始不再压迫人了呢？殖民地的历史才过去多久啊", "timestamp": 1628865112, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2271788, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 437233, "reply_to": 2271762, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 但殖民体系这种不自由不民主的东西终究会瓦解，拉美很早就推翻了殖民统治，亚非拉在二战后也都独立起来", "timestamp": 1628865274, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2271794, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 437233, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "民主很重要，但它仅仅是民主而已，它的最大优势是能提供统治合法性，在除此之外的领域，民主并不能被视作唯一的良药。很多国家的发展不是因为民主，而恰恰是因为民主之外的很多因素。", "timestamp": 1628865362, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2271800, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 437233, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "推荐赵鼎新《民主的限制》", "timestamp": 1628865402, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2271811, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 437233, "reply_to": 2271788, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 是啊，殖民地体系已经瓦解了，你觉得英国还能撑得住下一次世界大战嘛", "timestamp": 1628865504, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2271820, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 437233, "reply_to": 2271794, "tag": null, "text": "Re Isabella: 我没有说民主一定带来繁荣，但人类最终的归宿一定是民主", "timestamp": 1628865555, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2271821, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 437233, "reply_to": 2271788, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 美国又难道是依靠民主建立起今天的军事力量和债台嘛", "timestamp": 1628865573, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2271829, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 437233, "reply_to": 2271811, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 我不认为民主和经济繁荣之间有必然关系，但是历史已经证明，除了民主以外，人类几乎没有维持繁荣的方式", "timestamp": 1628865663, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2271838, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 437233, "reply_to": 2271821, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 我举了那么多例子是为了证明，人类可以通过不民主的方式取得繁荣，但所有不民主的繁荣都是暂时的，要么他们最终在民主下享受繁荣，要么像俄罗斯，土耳其一样日益衰微", "timestamp": 1628865772, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2271865, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 437233, "reply_to": 2271838, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 很有宿命论的感觉，个人希望人类能打破这一宿命吧", "timestamp": 1628865921, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2271866, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Jason", "pid": 437233, "reply_to": 2271838, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 民主和共产党不矛盾；新加坡的民主也是民主", "timestamp": 1628865934, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2271876, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Jason", "pid": 437233, "reply_to": 2271838, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 你不能因为新加坡一党独大就认为它不民主", "timestamp": 1628865975, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2271895, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 437233, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "上古时代的亚里士多德都能把政体分成六种，在这里就用民主不民主判断一个人类的宿命未免太武断且幼稚了", "timestamp": 1628866231, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2271917, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 437233, "reply_to": 2271895, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 你觉得人类的未来是走向缸中之脑全员梦游呢，还是失去控制自我毁灭呢\n总不能还走出星海了吧hhhh", "timestamp": 1628866436, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2271922, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 437233, "reply_to": 2271895, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 可是现代社会哪来的贵族制和君主制呢？", "timestamp": 1628866451, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2271972, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 437233, "reply_to": 2271917, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 我觉得你的问题是一个很大的维度，民主与否在里面的影响力太低了，尤其是dz提的这种发源于中世纪的民主", "timestamp": 1628866846, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2272002, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 437233, "reply_to": 2271922, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 我的意思是他这六类都已经够粗了，现代社会每个国家的情况更复杂，可以分的更细，单凭民主一个变量去解释可信度很低", "timestamp": 1628867086, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2272029, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 437233, "reply_to": 2272002, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 听dz的描述给了我一种妥协不妥协的感觉..", "timestamp": 1628867318, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2272035, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 437233, "reply_to": 2271972, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 基于此会有这样的想法", "timestamp": 1628867369, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2273798, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Kate", "pid": 437233, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "民主的表现形式是什么？其核心内涵是什么？民主制度是单一和固定的么？多数人的暴政又如何解决？", "timestamp": 1628900609, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2273985, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Louis", "pid": 437233, "reply_to": 2271672, "tag": null, "text": "看见英国因民主成功差点没把我笑死😆你不会觉得英国的成功跟民主有一毛钱关系吧？恰恰是殖民主义是英国成功的关键", "timestamp": 1628904729, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2274703, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Margaret", "pid": 437233, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "天命昭昭是吧😅天命在你，你急啥😅", "timestamp": 1628912412, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2275084, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Nathan", "pid": 437233, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "热知识，社会主义核心价值观里面也有民主😅", "timestamp": 1628916057, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2275407, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Olivia", "pid": 437233, "reply_to": 2273985, "tag": null, "text": "Re Louis: 不能更赞同", "timestamp": 1628919033, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 15, "pid": 437233, "reply": 43, "tag": "政治相关", "text": "自从1688年民主制度在英国率先取得成功并且为英国带来繁荣后，几百年来，人类历史上无数转瞬而逝的大国试图以非民主制度弯道超车：横跨三洲的奥斯曼，横扫欧陆的拿破仑，领土巨大的沙皇，中国的满洲皇帝，尚武的普鲁士，崇拜武士道的大和人，高举红旗的苏维埃等等，每个国家都用自己的道路在短期内实现了经济腾飞，并且成为世界上数一数二的强国，但是却在到达顶峰后因为各种原因迅速衰落，要么接受民主制度的改造，要么就此沉沦。\n如今，经济繁荣和政治不民主只在新加坡，香港等小岛上苟延残喘地并存。而下一个接受民主制度改造的伟大国家，会是？", "timestamp": 1628863698, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1628919033, "url": "", "vote": {}}}